    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but some people say the whole thing is basically just a tool for the big countries to do whatever they want, and that the UN is actually making things worse by giving them legitimacy to act that way. do historians generally see those critics as having a point, or is that just seen as a fringe view?",
